    "methodology": "Membership and asset figures are drawn from Bank of England regulatory returns and ABCUL voluntary reporting. Great Britain figures cover England, Scotland and Wales. Northern Ireland credit unions report separately to the PRA. International penetration rates are from the World Council of Credit Unions and use the economically active population as the denominator. Loan purpose breakdowns are estimated from ABCUL member surveys and may not be perfectly representative of all credit unions.",
